Package: TOSCA
Type: Package
Title: TOSCA - Timing Of Somatic Copy number Alterations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Alice", "Antonello", email = "alice.antonello@units.it", role=c("aut","cre")),
            person("Riccardo", "Bergamin", email = "riccardo.bergamin@units.it", role=c("aut")))
Maintainer: Alice Antonello <alice.antonello@units.it>
Description: TOSCA is a packege for inferring the timing in real time of clonal and subclonal somatic copy numbers (SCNA) of type 2:0, 2:1 and 2:2, from WGS longitudinal data. 
